s=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/17/02 2:40:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3316.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.mindspring.com/~cynnamin/eq/avalurra.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Escape from Lava</span><hr size=1> *sigh*  Necros should retire from the corpse summoning business <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mithlin>Mithlin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 145<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/17/02 3:17:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3316.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Escape from Lava</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Wait until you reach a bubble or less of health after falling in the lava, assuming you don't want to die and can't get out otherwise...then /q. You will 'die' while linkdead, but it will in fact just move you back to the inzone stripped of buffs with a bubble of health, kind of like if you 'die' while zoning.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
